lead_paragraph: Here is a document that Freedom Partners — a group organized and funded by the Koch brothers — released in early January, detailing what it hoped President Trump and Congress would do first, in terms of rolling back regulations, many of which impact the energy industry. Congress and Mr. Trump started to move through the list this past week.
